Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my name isn't Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you were brought into my \N hospital, your name was Anna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your brother's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.86,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,130)\pos(354,319)}House of Tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fortner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mauler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mauler!  Mr. Mauler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fornter!  It's me, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought Anna... I mean Nina back safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mauler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call the police from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no signs that the police were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mauler...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the cigarette that you loved so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mauler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed my brother back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone line has been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will come here to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We received a report and came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us look around a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either of you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements should be arriving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave the crime scene to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and have you two come down to \N the station to give a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she the daughter of the victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't get a look at the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought something like that would \N happen in a peaceful town like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What country are you from?  China?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you are from Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible situation to be in.  In a \N foreign country so far from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Heidelberg Station should be \N towards the middle of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came from the neighboring Mannheim Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they taking us to a station in another town?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be arriving in about fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They received a report?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they came because they \N received a report, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But whose report?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phone line was cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This car came without the siren on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the police remove the primary witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without first preserving the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... their police badges looked real...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could they...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could these men have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Officers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are looking for a hit and run driver, \N so I would like to ask for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn't Detectives Messner and Müller!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you heading back to the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is a brand new car!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be worn out soon enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...since we treat it badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, she said she's not feeling well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So can she go outside to get some fresh air?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, s-sure.  Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did those two do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they real detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about that blood stain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose report did they receive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they come without their siren on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you my name, but I never said I was a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a general store nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to get some clothes to change into.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some bread, sausage and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also had them fill the thermos with some warm coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you might not be hungry, but you have to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First things first.  You should get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of people... were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were walking among them together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was like we were the only \N two people left in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We crossed the border...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle and aunt cheered us up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were very kind to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then my brother said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that he had the perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my uncle and aunt died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, those who are kind to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...every one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I found out why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lieberts' case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother shot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... shot all those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother killed them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why... I picked up the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I aimed it at my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, he said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was laughing when he said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said to throw the gun out the window after I shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to aim straight for his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you had not saved my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Papa and Mama would not have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If those two detectives from last night were real...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would mean that Johan has \N connections with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't just stay here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is trying to take you away with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone comes after you, hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat well, drink the warm coffee, and take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how people live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any leads on the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(514,0)\pos(363,374)}Heidelberg Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any connections to the middle aged couple murders \N that have been occurring throughout the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, we are putting all our \N resources into the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I cannot give you any specific information at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to what we have learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Fortners had a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is also currently under investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was the reporter named Mauler also \N in their house when they were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the Japanese man seen together with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Japanese man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy smells suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the murder at Heidelberg Castle that occurred roughly \N at the same time the work of the same man?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heidelberg Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was killed, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, detailed information will \N be given out when we are ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming all the way from the \N Mannheim Station to help us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will really help, Detectives Messner and Müller!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let us know what you want us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the current status of the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us discuss this thoroughly inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were real!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those men... were real detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Heidelberg Post.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The editorial department is packed right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you guys keep it down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring an important witness with \N me and be there at 5 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not report this to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.59,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?  This is not some kind of false lead, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't go to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...only the newspaper is left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the only place that can ensure Nina's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mauler...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.94,0:18:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't come into the room without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, even though you are from the BKA,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are here to investigate the murders \N of the middle aged couples, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have material on the man who \N was killed at Heidelberg Castle here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.01,0:19:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your case and this one both happened at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not done by the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man has the marks that suggest he was bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find rope or something nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the victim was found, his \N hands were already untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are four routes from which \N to escape the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...somewhere he wouldn't be suspected of going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the footpath as his escape route...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The well lit walkway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is me, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to hide anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should not have left her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma, it is not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only performed your duty as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please eat the sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And please, get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... please save as many lives as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me who brought him back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me who brought that monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...back to life!
